videos.headline: McCrae runs it in to get UCF on the board
videos.description: Greg McCrae gets the direct snap and bounces to the outside for a 1-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McCrae runs it in to get UCF on the board) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pinnix find end zone for East Carolina's 1st TD
videos.description: Darius Pinnix gets the short pass from Holton Ahlers and finds the end zone from 17 yards out.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pinnix find end zone for East Carolina’s 1st TD) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCF's Robinson hauls in the 64-yard TD
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel launches the ball downfield to an open Jaylon Robinson to extend UCF's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCF’s Robinson hauls in the 64-yard TD) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCF's Hescock throws the stiff arm and gets a TD that counts
videos.description: After his first touchdown was called back due to a flag, Jake Hescock gets this 7-yard touchdown with no issues.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCF’s Hescock throws the stiff arm and gets a TD that counts ) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCF's Harris makes scoring look easy
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel passes over the middle to Jacob Harris who gets the easy 11-yard touchdown reception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCF’s Harris makes scoring look easy) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCF's Gabriel connects with Robinson for another TD
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel finds Jaylon Robinson in the back of the end zone for the 9-yard touchdown, his second of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCF’s Gabriel connects with Robinson for another TD) 2020/09/26 ESHEET
